sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor A as Operator
    participant V as Vault OCI Credential Engine
    participant P as Published HTTPS JWKS Location
    participant O as OCI Identity Domain

    A->>V: `vault read -format=json oci/jwks`
    V-->>A: JWKS document for active self-mint signing key
    A->>P: Publish JWKS JSON to HTTPS location
    A->>O: Configure token exchange trust with JWKS URL
    O->>P: Fetch JWKS during trust evaluation / key discovery
    P-->>O: Public keys only
